mecca.meccurator

Class Art

  • java.lang.Object
    • mecca.meccurator.Art

  • public class Art
extends java.lang.Object
    Each art object has its own bid list attribute to keep track of the bids that have been placed on it. Possible statuses are: available, bidded, or borrowed.
